Package org.schema.game.client.view.buildhelper

This package contains every class related to BuildHelpers.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildHelper
    The class all BuildHelpers have to extend from.
    CircleBuildHelper  
    EllipsoidBuildHelper
    The BuildHelper for generating ellipsoids.
    TorusBuildHelper
    The BuildHelper for tori.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    BuildHelperClass
    Every class extending a BuildHelper, that the user should be able to select, must annotate this annotation.
    BuildHelperVar
    Every field used for user input in a BuildHelper has to annotate this annotation
